Euro Group Chief Juncker Says EFSF Ceiling Shouldn’t Be Raised

-- B y   J o n a t h a n   S t e a r n s
-- 
2011-10-03T22:29:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-03/euro-group-chief-juncker-says-efsf-ceiling-shouldn-t-be-raised.html
Luxembourg’s  Jean-Claude Juncker , who
leads the group of euro-area finance ministers, said the ceiling
of the region’s temporary rescue fund shouldn’t be raised. He
spoke to reporters in Luxembourg today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jonathan Stearns in Luxembourg at 
